    11â†’ * 3. Generates license keys via the existing licenseService
    12â†’ * 4. Sets up "team" tier for full feature access
    13â†’ * 
    14â†’ * Usage:
    15â†’ *   STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxx DATABASE_URL=xxx node scripts/setup-beta-testers.js
